[![PyPI](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/qBitrr2?label=PyPI)](https://pypi.org/project/qBitrr2/)
[![Downloads](https://img.shields.io/pypi/dm/qBitrr2)](https://pypi.org/project/qBitrr2/)
